<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-05-16T09:29:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-05-16T09:29:00-05:00" n="213" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d213">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.00/1839</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Consul at Moscow</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_PDC1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Poole</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Moscow</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-05-16T17:00:00+02:31"><hi rend="italic">May 16,
                                            1918, 5 p.m.</hi></date>
                                    <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received May 23, 12.01
                                    p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>524. <persName corresp="#p_JD1">Jenkins</persName><note n="1" xml:id="d213fn1"><persName corresp="#p_JD1">Douglas
                                        Jenkins</persName>, Consul at Riga, on detail in
                                    Siberia.</note> telegraphs, 14th, advance of <persName corresp="#p_SGG1">Semenov</persName> has apparently been checked
                                for the present. He is evidently trying to strengthen his positions.
                                Bolsheviks have been considerably reenforced, principally by
                                prisoners.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed><persName corresp="#p_PDC1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Poole</hi></persName></signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>